                <p style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;text-align:justify;line-height:  normal;'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#212529;'><br> <strong>İşlenme Şartları</strong></span></p>
            </td>
            <td style="padding:0in 0in 0in 0in;">
                <p style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:0in;font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;'><strong><span style='font-family:  "Times New Roman",serif;color:#212529;'>Kapsamı</span></strong></p>
            </td>
            <td style="padding:0in 0in 0in 0in;">
                <p style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:0in;font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;'><strong><span style='font-family:  "Times New Roman",serif;color:#212529;'>&Ouml;rnek</span></strong></p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding:0in 0in 0in 0in;">
                <p style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:0in;font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;'><strong><span style='font-family:  "Times New Roman",serif;color:#212529;'>Kanun H&uuml;km&uuml;</span></strong></p>
            </td>
            <td style="padding:0in 0in 0in 0in;">
                <p style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:0in;font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:#212529;'>Vergi Mevzuatı, İş Mevzuatı,Ticaret Mevzuatı vb.</span></p>
